Application management in Microsoft Entra ID enables administrators to control how applications integrate with identity systems.

Capabilities include:

* App registration
* Enterprise applications
* Access permissions
* User consent policies

For example, administrators can configure authentication for custom business apps.

A real-life use case is managing access to third-party SaaS tools like ServiceNow or Slack.

Another example is securing APIs with Entra-based authentication.

Application management ensures secure and centralized control.
